headline: Should You Buy Starbucks Stock Right Now?
summary: Like caffeine intake's impact on the body throughout the day, Starbucks (NASDAQ: SBUX) has taken its investors on an up-and-down journey in the past 12 months.  Here's what investors need to know about Starbucks before making an informed decision.  Starbucks has become a well-known brand in the restaurant space.
